    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The sync mechanism for light client is not delivered yet. So theoretically light client won't work after the merge. However, technically it can still sync *without* beacon client, but it's not safe at all without consensus security guarantee. In another word, it blindly trusts the ethereum full node.\r\n\r\nSo if you only want to retrieve some data without high security requirement, maybe you can try it, otherwise I will recommend you to switch fullnode until we deliver the PoS-complete light client.",
